{"id": "art-1461", "label": "Art. 1461", "title": "Art. 1461: Obţinerea datelor privind tranzacţiile financiare ale unei persoane", "slug": "art-1461", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_247147554\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2456\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_247147554\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 146<sup>1</sup>:\nOb&#355;inerea datelor privind tranzac&#355;iile financiare ale unei persoane </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1479923554\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2455\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1479923554\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Ob&#355;inerea\ndatelor privind tranzac&#355;iile financiare efectuate se poate dispune de\njudec&#259;torul de drepturi &#351;i libert&#259;&#355;i de la instan&#355;a\nc&#259;reia i-ar reveni competen&#355;a s&#259; judece cauza în prim&#259;\ninstan&#355;&#259; sau de la instan&#355;a corespunz&#259;toare în grad\nacesteia în a c&#259;rei circumscrip&#355;ie se afl&#259; sediul parchetului\ndin care face parte procurorul care a întocmit propunerea, cu privire la\ntranzac&#355;iile financiare ale f&#259;ptuitorului, suspectului, inculpatului\nsau ale oric&#259;rei persoane care este b&#259;nuit&#259; c&#259;\nrealizeaz&#259; asemenea opera&#355;iuni cu f&#259;ptuitorul, suspectul sau\ninculpatul, dac&#259;:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2138866665\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2454\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2138866665\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)exist&#259; o suspiciune rezonabil&#259; cu privire la\npreg&#259;tirea sau s&#259;vâr&#351;irea unei infrac&#355;iuni;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_698961627\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2453\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_698961627\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)m&#259;sura este necesar&#259; &#351;i\npropor&#355;ional&#259; cu restrângerea drepturilor &#351;i\nlibert&#259;&#355;ilor fundamentale, date fiind particularit&#259;&#355;ile\ncauzei, importan&#355;a informa&#355;iilor sau a probelor ce urmeaz&#259; a fi\nob&#355;inute ori gravitatea infrac&#355;iunii;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_594592498\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2452\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_594592498\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)probele nu ar putea fi ob&#355;inute în alt mod sau\nob&#355;inerea lor ar presupune dificult&#259;&#355;i deosebite ce ar\nprejudicia ancheta ori exist&#259; un pericol pentru siguran&#355;a persoanelor\nsau a unor bunuri de valoare.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1033576764\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2451\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1033576764\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Ob&#355;inerea datelor privind tranzac&#355;iile\nfinanciare ce urmeaz&#259; a fi efectuate poate fi dispus&#259; pe o\ndurat&#259; de cel mult 30 de zile de judec&#259;torul de drepturi &#351;i\nlibert&#259;&#355;i de la instan&#355;a c&#259;reia i-ar reveni competen&#355;a\ns&#259; judece cauza în prim&#259; instan&#355;&#259; sau de la instan&#355;a\ncorespunz&#259;toare în grad acesteia în a c&#259;rei circumscrip&#355;ie se\nafl&#259; sediul parchetului din care face parte procurorul care a întocmit propunerea,\ndac&#259; sunt îndeplinite condi&#355;iile prev&#259;zute la alin. (1).</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_11188212\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2450\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_11188212\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Dispozi&#355;iile art. 140 alin. (2)-(9) se aplic&#259;\nîn mod corespunz&#259;tor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_216754701\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2449\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_216754701\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Mandatul prin care este autorizat&#259; ob&#355;inerea\ndatelor privind tranzac&#355;iile financiare ce urmeaz&#259; a fi efectuate\npoate fi prelungit în condi&#355;iile art. 144, durata total&#259; a\nm&#259;surii neputând dep&#259;&#351;i, în aceea&#351;i cauz&#259; &#351;i cu\nprivire la aceea&#351;i persoan&#259;, 6 luni.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1347363098\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2448\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1347363098\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)În cazurile în care exist&#259; urgen&#355;&#259;, iar\nob&#355;inerea mandatului în condi&#355;iile alin. (1) sau (2) ar conduce la o\nîntârziere substan&#355;ial&#259; a cercet&#259;rilor, la pierderea, alterarea\nsau distrugerea probelor ori ar pune în pericol siguran&#355;a victimei sau a\naltor persoane &#351;i sunt îndeplinite condi&#355;iile prev&#259;zute la alin.\n(1) sau, dup&#259; caz, alin. (2), procurorul poate dispune ob&#355;inerea\ndatelor privind tranzac&#355;iile financiare efectuate sau care urmeaz&#259; a\nfi efectuate. Dispozi&#355;iile art. 141 se aplic&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_598442370\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2447\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_598442370\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)Este interzis&#259; ob&#355;inerea datelor privind\ntranzac&#355;iile financiare dintre avocat &#351;i suspect, inculpat sau orice\nalt&#259; persoan&#259; pe care acesta o ap&#259;r&#259;, cu excep&#355;ia\nsitua&#355;iilor în care exist&#259; date c&#259; avocatul\ns&#259;vâr&#351;e&#351;te sau preg&#259;te&#351;te s&#259;vâr&#351;irea unei\ninfrac&#355;iuni dintre cele prev&#259;zute la art. 139 alin. (2).</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_744593516\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2446\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_744593516\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)institu&#355;iile de credit sau entit&#259;&#355;ile\nfinanciare care efectueaz&#259; tranzac&#355;iile financiare sunt obligate\ns&#259; predea înscrisurile sau informa&#355;iile la care se face referire în\nmandatul dispus de judec&#259;tor sau în autoriza&#355;ia emis&#259; de\nprocuror.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_487925644\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2445\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_487925644\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(8)Dispozi&#355;iile art. 145 &#351;i 145<sup>1</sup> se\naplic&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2126225001\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2444\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2126225001\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(9)[textul din Art. 146^1, alin. (9) din partea 1, titlul\nIV, capitolul IV a fost abrogat la 09-iul-2023 de </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>Art. I, punctul 21. din Legea 201/2023</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>]</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_121082783\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2443\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_121082783\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>*) Curtea Constitu&#355;ional&#259; admite excep&#355;ia de\nneconstitu&#355;ionalitate &#351;i constat&#259; c&#259; solu&#355;ia\nlegislativ&#259; cuprins&#259; în dispozi&#355;iile art. 146<sup>1</sup>Codul\nde procedur&#259; penal&#259;, care nu permite contestarea\nlegalit&#259;&#355;ii m&#259;surii referitoare la ob&#355;inerea datelor\nprivind tranzac&#355;iile financiare ale unei persoane de c&#259;tre persoana\nvizat&#259; de aceasta, care nu are calitatea de inculpat, este\nneconstitu&#355;ional&#259;.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}